<p>
  When set, only users who have identified with NickServ can join the channel. Users already in the channel when +R is set are not affected.
</p>
<.help_h4 icon={:icon_terminal}>Usage</.help_h4>
<pre>/mode +R    — Enable registered-only mode
/mode -R    — Disable registered-only mode</pre>
<.help_h4 icon={:icon_link}>See Also</.help_h4>
<p><.help_link topic="feature-nickserv">NickServ</.help_link></p>
